start_012c3b85	tu_unknown	A honey bee, to be exact! But yes!	game/script.rpy	34	tu_unknown "[what]"
start_4ca72723	tu_unknown	Hello hello! So glad you're here. I'm absolutely buzzing with excitement!	game/script.rpy	36	tu_unknown "[what]"
